The ability of my scanner:
	My scanner implements the spec of HW1.

Environment:
	Linux workstation of CS

How to run my scanner:
	1. put scanner.l and Makefile in same directory.
	2. type "make" to build the scanner executable.
	3. You can run scanner without parameters, 
	   and the scanner will scan the stdin and output the token string;
	   or you can run scanner with one filename, 
	   and the scanner will scan this file and output the token string.
